output:
 以下のコードを使用して、以前の購入履歴に基づいて興味があると思われる関連製品を紹介する販売メールを作成します。これらの製品が購入にふさわしい理由を強調します。
// Create a new message.
var message = new Message();
// Add a subject.
message.Subject = "Related products";
// Add a plain text body.
message.Body = "Dear customer,

We noticed that you recently purchased a product from us. We thought you might be interested in some related products that we think you might like.

Product 1: This product is great for... 

Product 2: This product is great for... 

Product 3: This product is great for... 

We hope you find these products useful. If you have any questions or concerns, please don't hesitate to contact us.

Regards,
Your Company";
// Add a HTML body.
message.HtmlBody = "<html><body><p>Dear customer,</p><p>We noticed that you recently purchased a product from us. We thought you might be interested in some related products that we think you might like.</p><p><b>Product 1:</b> This product is great for...</p><p><b>Product 2:</b> This product is great for...</p><p><b>Product 3:</b> This product is great for...</p><p>We hope you find these products useful. If you have any questions or concerns, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p><p>Regards,</p><p>Your Company</p></body></html>";
// Add a recipient.
message.To.Add(new MailAddress("customer@example.com"));
// Send the message.
message.Send();
